{"tid":1096629,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！BORDERLAND 開發裔GEARBOX 怒屌 STEAM 以及玩家！","createTime":"2019-04-07T23:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T23:44:46.000Z","uid":33359,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"78bd08e1a8f489f710498c8ad05c214f9a5d5c73","tid":1096629,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:53:56.000Z","msg":"最近因為《無主之地3》PC版Epic限時獨占導致憤怒的玩家去Steam上給前兩部遊戲狂刷差評。對此，Gearbox CEO Randy Pitchford表示Steam允許玩家狂刷差評的行徑讓他對《無主之地3》Epic商城獨占的觀點更加堅定，甚至爆了粗口和玩家對噴起來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nga.178.com/attachments/mon_201904/07/-7Q5-gifK1nT1kShj-kx.jpeg.medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nga.178.com%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201904%2F07%2F-7Q5-gifK1nT1kShj-kx.jpeg.medium.jpg&h=20d7d4b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;諷刺的是，這種濫用是可以發生的，Steam根本沒有興趣去糾正這種濫用，這讓我對2K的選擇感到有點高興，讓我不得不重新考慮我們對Steam的發行計劃。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n然而，Randy Pitchford的回复顯然有一部分是錯誤的。早在上個月15號Steam為了打擊差評轟炸就修改了遊戲的用戶評分系統，而且《無主之地2》還是首個受益遊戲。無論玩家怎麼狂刷差評，Steam上的《無主之地2》評分仍然是&ldquo;特別好評&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\nRandy Pitchford推文發布後，不少國外玩家進行了回復反擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nga.178.com/attachments/mon_201904/07/-7Q5-dsyvK1aT1kShf-ge.jpeg.medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nga.178.com%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201904%2F07%2F-7Q5-dsyvK1aT1kShf-ge.jpeg.medium.jpg&h=3863c9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有玩家表示，&ldquo;《無主之地2》被差評轟炸還不是因為你們自己搞獨占交易。這是你們自作自受。你，2K還是其他人，玩家這麼憤怒都是因為你們。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對此，Pitchford非常生氣地爆粗口回复說：&ldquo;如果你不值得的話，我就不會打你。我打你是你的錯。這是什麼狗屁理論，滿嘴狗屎。滾一邊去。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n玩家Matto回复說：&ldquo;你這是讓事情退步了。真相是這些年開發商和發行商濫用與玩家的關係，但現在玩家們已經厭倦了被餵屎，他們正在反擊。你個蠢逼才不是受害者，你們是作惡者。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nga.178.com/attachments/mon_201904/07/-7Q5-ip93K1qT1kSh9-jh.jpeg.medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nga.178.com%2Fattachments%2Fmon_201904%2F07%2F-7Q5-ip93K1qT1kSh9-jh.jpeg.medium.jpg&h=16af3886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於玩家刷差評，前《半條命2》編劇Chet Faliszek(目前是Stray Bombay工作室聯合創始人)給出了自己的看法。他認為玩家差評轟炸越來越反映出玩家們的無奈，他們沒有一個和開發者溝通的有效手段，讓開發者聽到自己的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載原地址:[<a href=\"https://rm.mbd.baidu.com/5gmb255?f=cp]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frm.mbd.baidu.com%2F5gmb255%3Ff%3Dcp%5D&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=6e4a37d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rm.mbd.baidu.com/5gmb255?f=cp]</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?&amp;tid=16887245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.nga.cn%2Fread.php%3F%26tid%3D16887245&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUTY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=cf708c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?&amp;tid=16887245</a>"},{"pid":"e30e70fc3412f35b393c037ecb8975a186c9faca","tid":1096629,"uid":23363,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:57:30.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔係steam上game囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過epic 同uplay 對比起steam<br />\n質素係點大家有目共睹<br />\n到時多bug多掛整死隻game無人買唔好喊"},{"pid":"b238ac809a5d9be45766f9d297e95131da3ea886","tid":1096629,"uid":136038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"印仔好早<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddaa4a93fa4763304fdb802b32f6978378608cb","tid":1096629,"uid":51701,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:58:28.000Z","msg":"支那spyware<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4270153843b5d022529470cb7bc234a2c54c662","tid":1096629,"uid":177783,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:58:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ff67c46646e30b172c96384dfdcdd99f2835ac8","tid":1096629,"uid":177783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T23:58:56.000Z",